race.comment: TALLADEGA GIRL (9) returned from a break and led throughout for a strong win. Carries the same weight here after the claim and fitter again. Has good upside and is expected to take catching. ASMITA (14) was good fresh when runner-up then was not too far away but failed to threaten in the latest. Has a much better gate this time though and is capable of sharp improvement. FLITGROVE (6) resumed from a long break with a close-up fifth. Tough draw to overcome but strips fitter and well placed this level. INTIMEOFNEED (12) was another who ran well two back then disappointed last time. That has been a strong form race though and a senior rider goes on this time. Can bounce back. DOUBT IN THE SKY (10) is a progressive filly who was placed fresh then scored her maiden win last time. Up a notch here but improving with each run and can measure up again.
